== 歷年事件 ==
=== 1993年科羅拉多州奧羅拉槍擊事件 ===
1993年12月14日，[[美國|美國]][[科羅拉多州|科羅拉多州]][[奥罗拉_(科罗拉多州)|奧羅拉]]的出奇老鼠分店有四名員工在店內突然被持用二五口徑[[手槍|手槍]]的歹徒槍殺致死，第五名員工受重傷。犯案人是餐廳的前任員工，當年19歲的內森·杰拉德·鄧拉普（Nathan Jerard Dunlap）因在槍擊事件發生前五個月在餐廳工作被解僱感到沮喪，並決定發動突襲報仇。他帶著贓物和飯店物品逃離槍擊案現場。被捕後他被判犯有四項[[美國法律|美國法律]]的一級[[謀殺|謀殺]]罪<ref>{{Cite web|title=一級謀殺(罪),murder in the first degree,元照英美法詞典 － 免費線上查詢!|url=http://lawyer.get.com.tw/Dic/DictionaryDetail.aspx?iDT=65197|accessdate=2019-11-24|work=lawyer.get.com.tw}}</ref>，[[未遂|未遂]]謀殺罪和其他罪刑，並於1996年5月17日被判[[電椅|電椅死刑]]。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Nathan Dunlap on death row for Chuck E. Cheese killings|url=https://www.cnn.com/2014/07/31/us/death-row-stories-dunlap/index.html|accessdate=2019-11-24|last=CNN|first=By Thom Patterson|work=CNN|dead-url=no|archive-date=2020-04-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200426034056/https://www.cnn.com/2014/07/31/us/death-row-stories-dunlap/index.html}}</ref>法官原定2013年8月為他死刑執行日期，但科羅拉多州[[州長_(美國)|州長]][[約翰·希肯盧珀|約翰·希肯盧珀]]為他簽署了[[緩刑|臨時緩刑]]，這將延遲了鄧拉普的處決日期。<ref>{{Cite journal|title=1993 Aurora, Colorado, shooting|url=https://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=1993_Aurora,_Colorado,_shooting&oldid=924200137|date=2019-11-02|journal=Wikipedia|language=en}}</ref>

===2019年陰謀論事件===
在2019年1月和2019年2月，[[美國|美國]][[Youtuber|Youtuber]][[谢恩·多森|谢恩·多森]]在個人頻道上的[[陰謀論|陰謀論]]系列發布了有關出奇老鼠餐廳的陰謀論，稱出奇老鼠餐廳部分門市會回收顧客吃不完的披薩並把他們重組拼成完整的披薩端給顧客，理由是披薩每一片的大小外形有點不同，使在美國網路界引起討論，甚至上了美國電視[[脫口秀|脫口秀]]節目《[[艾倫·狄珍妮秀|艾倫·狄珍妮秀]]》<ref>{{Citation|title=Investigating Conspiracies with Shane Dawson|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=sNuKpwX6Tz4|accessdate=2019-11-25|language=zh-CN|archive-date=2019-11-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191124232103/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=sNuKpwX6Tz4|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Shane Dawson releases highly-anticipated second episode of Conspiracy Series on YouTube|url=https://www.dexerto.com/entertainment/shane-dawson-releases-highly-anticipated-second-episode-conspiracy-series-youtube-353838|accessdate=2019-11-24|work=Dexerto.com|dead-url=no|archive-date=2019-02-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190213015752/https://www.dexerto.com/entertainment/shane-dawson-releases-highly-anticipated-second-episode-conspiracy-series-youtube-353838}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Chuck E. Cheese's denies recycling old pizzas after viral video|url=https://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-6697983/Chuck-E-Cheese-denies-recycling-old-pizzas-viral-video.html|accessdate=2019-11-24|date=2019-02-13|work=Mail Online|archive-date=2021-06-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210623004724/https://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-6697983/Chuck-E-Cheese-denies-recycling-old-pizzas-viral-video.html}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=UMMM SO THE CHUCK E CHEESE CONSPIRACY MADE IT TO THE ELLEN SHOW @shanedawsonpic.twitter.com/xs1RUoTO9V|url=https://twitter.com/oneearedweasley/status/1098312143886319618|accessdate=2019-11-24|date=2019-02-20|last=Mikayla ✨|work=@oneearedweasley|language=en}}</ref><ref>{{Citation|title=ELLEN CHIMES IN ON CHUCK E CHEESE PIZZA CONSPIRACY|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=UfO9E8ppJnQ|accessdate=2019-11-24|language=zh-CN|archive-date=2019-02-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190221105217/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=UfO9E8ppJnQ&gl=US&hl=en|dead-url=no}}</ref>，整體事件對出奇老鼠餐廳的名譽產生影響，造成謝恩一度被出奇老鼠起訴。而出奇老鼠在2019年2月13日於官方[[推特|推特]]解釋他們不回收顧客吃不完的食物：<ref>{{Cite web|title=No conspiracies here – the stories going around about Chuck E. Cheese's and our pizza are absolutely untrue. We make our pizzas to order fresh with dough made in house. Sometimes that means the pizza doesn't look perfect, but it still tastes delicious.|url=https://twitter.com/ChuckECheese/status/1095460128759996417|accessdate=2019-11-25|date=2019-02-12|last=Cheese|first=Chuck E.|work=@ChuckECheese|language=en|dead-url=no|archive-date=2020-06-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200611171407/https://twitter.com/ChuckECheese/status/1095460128759996417}}</ref>
{{Cquote|這裡沒有陰謀 – 關於我們披薩的故事是絕對不真實的。我們使用自製的麵團使披薩新鮮。有時這意味著披薩看起來並不完美，但仍然味道鮮美。 (No conspiracies here – the stories going around about Chuck E. Cheese's and our pizza are absolutely untrue. We make our pizzas to order fresh with dough made in house. Sometimes that means the pizza doesn't look perfect, but it still tastes delicious.)}}
另有前餐廳員工向外國媒體表示：「在那兒的那幾年，我從未見過披薩被送回廚房然後回收給顧客，即使是客人還沒開始吃到的披薩，也總是把那些披薩丟掉。」、「披薩看起來如此奇怪的原因是切割工具並不總是完全穿過(披薩)，導致不規則的切割痕跡，餡餅還會在烤箱中改變形狀。」、「當比薩餅穿過烤箱時，比薩餅會收縮。披薩餅會翹曲，並且取決於奶酪或餡醬的數量，其大小和形狀會有所不同，因此，披薩切片的長度並不總是相同的。」<ref>{{Cite web|title=Despite Shane Dawson's Latest Video, Chuck E Cheese's Says All Its Pizzas Are Made Fresh|url=https://www.buzzfeednews.com/article/laurenstrapagiel/shane-dawson-chuck-e-cheeses-pizza|accessdate=2019-11-25|work=BuzzFeed News|language=en|dead-url=no|archive-date=2019-12-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191211073229/https://www.buzzfeednews.com/article/laurenstrapagiel/shane-dawson-chuck-e-cheeses-pizza}}</ref>

